title: Magenta Gold 7.2.0 (by hristoforos)
description:
magenta gold 7.2.0 is probably the best dictionary that in my opinion is out there.

i try it in my windows 8 64 bit and it works like a charm.

i try many dictionaries that i have downloaded but this is the only one that did the job.
 
perfect for sentences and not only for single words like all the others.

for example:i put "voluntary manslaughter" and i translated in greek.

it came out exactly the way it was supposed too.with the exact same meaning of it. 

so i strongly recommend it!
